This government bit the bullet. 
Now we are rewarding Canadians for their hard work by making those tax cuts.  
Mr. Peter Stoffer (Sackville-Musquodoboit Valley-Eastern Shore, NDP):
Madam Speaker, again I listened intently to my colleague from the Liberal Party. 
